---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = "January 2026";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for AllisonMurrayRealtor.com. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
>
  <section class="section legal">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="legal__updated">Last Updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="legal__content">
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          Allison Murray ("I", "me", or "my") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting
          your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how I collect, use, and safeguard
          information when you visit my website AllisonMurrayRealtor.com (the "Site") or contact me
          for real estate services.
        </p>

        <h2>Information I Collect</h2>
        <h3>Information You Provide</h3>
        <p>When you fill out a contact form, request a home valuation, or otherwise communicate with me, I may collect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Name and contact information (email address, phone number)</li>
          <li>Property address (for home valuations)</li>
          <li>Information about your real estate needs and preferences</li>
          <li>Any other information you choose to provide</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Information Collected Automatically</h3>
        <p>When you visit the Site, I may automatically collect certain information, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>IP address and browser type</li>
          <li>Pages visited and time spent on the Site</li>
          <li>Referring website or source</li>
          <li>Device information</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This information is collected through cookies and similar technologies, including Google Analytics.</p>

        <h2>How I Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>I use the information I collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Respond to your inquiries and provide real estate services</li>
          <li>Provide home valuations and market analysis</li>
          <li>Send you information about properties that may interest you (with your consent)</li>
          <li>Improve and optimize the Site</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Information Sharing</h2>
        <p>
          I do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. I may share your
          information with:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Chinatti Realty Group (my brokerage) as necessary to provide real estate services</li>
          <li>Service providers who help me operate the Site (e.g., hosting, email services)</li>
          <li>Legal authorities when required by law</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
        <p>
          The Site uses cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your experience.
          You can control cookies through your browser settings. I use:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Essential cookies:</strong> Required for the Site to function properly</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics cookies:</strong> Google Analytics to understand how visitors use the Site</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Google Analytics</h2>
        <p>
          I use Google Analytics to collect information about how visitors use the Site. Google Analytics
          uses cookies to collect information such as how often users visit, what pages they visit, and
          what other sites they visited before coming here. I use this information to improve the Site.
          You can opt out of Google Analytics by installing the
          <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          I take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access,
          use, or disclosure. However, no internet transmission is completely secure, and I cannot
          guarantee the security of information transmitted to the Site.
        </p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal information I hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your information</li>
          <li>Opt out of marketing communications</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          To exercise these rights, please contact me using the information below.
        </p>

        <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>
          The Site may contain links to third-party websites. I am not responsible for the privacy
          practices of these websites. I encourage you to review their privacy policies.
        </p>

        <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          The Site is not directed to children under 13, and I do not knowingly collect personal
          information from children under 13.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          I may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The updated policy will be posted
          on this page with a new "Last Updated" date.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact Me</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or wish to exercise your privacy rights,
          please contact me:
        </p>
        <ul class="legal__contact">
          <li><strong>Allison Murray, Realtor</strong></li>
          <li>Chinatti Realty Group</li>
          <li>Phone: <a href="tel:9788887649">(978) 888-7649</a></li>
          <li>Email: <a href="mailto:allison@chinattirealty.com">allison@chinattirealty.com</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal {
    padding-top: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .legal h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .legal__updated {
    color: var(--color-gray);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-light-gray);
  }

  .legal__content h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: var(--spacing-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .legal__content h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .legal__content p {
    color: var(--color-dark-gray);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .legal__content ul {
    margin-left: var(--spacing-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .legal__content li {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
    color: var(--color-dark-gray);
  }

  .legal__content a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .legal__content a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .legal__contact {
    list-style: none;
    margin-left: 0;
    background-color: var(--color-off-white);
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .legal__contact li {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .legal__contact li:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
</style>
